rgence to a single mode. Applications include discovering multiple winning strategies in RL, generating diverse molecules with similar binding affinity, or creating varied neural architectures with comparable accuracy. Theoretically, we derive bounds on performance loss relative to the global optimum under bounded embedding distortion, linking geometric properties of the behavioral manifold to solution reliability. Empirically, we demonstrate superior performance-diversity Pareto fronts compared to DGPO, MAP-Elites, and PE-DBO across domains.",
